! Summary

Adds custom controls to the GSDPanel for Projects.

! Detail

The `$:/tags/GSD5ProjectPlugin` tag is used to provide a end-user interface in [[Project]] tiddlers.  A tiddler with this tag will have its contents rendered in the right column of the [[GSDPanel]].

! Best Practice

* If creating custom controls prefer this tag over [[$:/tags/GSD5ProjectCore|GSD5ProjectCore]].
